data.description: This is an amazing detached split level corner property, with a deck and a patio,  just waiting for that wonderful buyer to enjoy. On the main level, there are three bedrooms, two full bathrooms, one large living room and dining room combined, with a large deck off the dining room, next to the eat-in kitchen that has ample custom cabinets, granite countertops and modern appliances. There is a large family room on the lower level, with a patio, great for family entertainment, as well as a small room that would be wonderful to use as an office or a yoga room.  Each room has controlled individual electric heating, to save on the energy bills. This property has an attached two car garage and a driveway that has four additional parking spaces, as well as on street parking. Property is located in a great school district, very convenient to shopping areas, restaurants and the local thoroughfare (Route 422) to many shopping outlets. This property will not last, it is definitely a first time buyer's dream and the dream of homeownership. Come see for yourself and make an offer.
